---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { withBase } from '../utils/urls';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for Valyrian News Network - how we handle your data.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <header class="mb-12 animate-fade-in-up">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-vnn-muted mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-vnn-ink mb-4 tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-vnn-gray font-body">
        Last updated: April 2, 2026
      </p>
    </header>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-10">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-4">Introduction</h2>
        <p class="text-vnn-charcoal leading-relaxed">
          Valyrian News Network ("VNN", "we", "us", or "our"), operated by Valyrian Tech BV, is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit our website and use our services.
        </p>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-3">Push Notification Subscriptions</h3>
        <p class="text-vnn-charcoal leading-relaxed mb-4">
          If you choose to subscribe to push notifications, we collect:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-vnn-gray space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li>• <strong>Push subscription endpoint:</strong> A URL provided by your browser to deliver notifications</li>
          <li>• <strong>Encryption keys:</strong> Required to securely send notifications to your device</li>
          <li>• <strong>Country preferences:</strong> The countries you select to receive notifications about</li>
          <li>• <strong>Patreon account information:</strong> Your Patreon user ID and membership status (to verify your subscription)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-3 mt-6">Website Usage</h3>
        <p class="text-vnn-charcoal leading-relaxed">
          Our website is hosted on GitHub Pages. We do not use cookies or tracking scripts. GitHub may collect basic server logs as described in their privacy policy.
        </p>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="text-vnn-charcoal leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We use the information we collect to:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-vnn-gray space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li>• Send you push notifications about new articles matching your country preferences</li>
          <li>• Verify your Patreon membership status</li>
          <li>• Improve our notification service</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-vnn-charcoal leading-relaxed mt-4">
          We do <strong>not</strong> sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.
        </p>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-4">Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <p class="text-vnn-charcoal leading-relaxed">
          Your push notification subscription data is stored securely using Cloudflare's infrastructure. We implement appropriate technical measures to protect your information against unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction.
        </p>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="text-vnn-charcoal leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We use the following third-party services:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-vnn-gray space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li>• <strong>GitHub Pages:</strong> Website hosting</li>
          <li>• <strong>Cloudflare:</strong> Push notification infrastructure</li>
          <li>• <strong>Patreon:</strong> Membership verification (OAuth)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-vnn-charcoal leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Each of these services has their own privacy policy governing their use of data.
        </p>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-vnn-charcoal leading-relaxed mb-4">
          You have the right to:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-vnn-gray space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li>• <strong>Unsubscribe:</strong> You can unsubscribe from push notifications at any time through your browser settings or our website</li>
          <li>• <strong>Access:</strong> Request information about the data we hold about you</li>
          <li>• <strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your subscription data</li>
          <li>• <strong>Correction:</strong> Update your country preferences at any time</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-vnn-charcoal leading-relaxed mt-4">
          To exercise these rights, contact us through our website.
        </p>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-4">Data Retention</h2>
        <p class="text-vnn-charcoal leading-relaxed">
          We retain your push notification subscription data for as long as you remain subscribed. If you unsubscribe or your Patreon membership lapses, we delete your subscription data within 30 days.
        </p>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-vnn-charcoal leading-relaxed">
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.
        </p>
      </section>
      
      <section class="bg-vnn-paper border border-vnn-rule p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-vnn-ink mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-vnn-gray">
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact Valyrian Tech BV through our <a href={withBase('/about')} class="text-vnn-vermillion">About page</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
      
      <footer class="text-center text-vnn-gray text-sm pt-8 hairline-top">
        <a href={withBase('/')} class="text-vnn-vermillion hover:underline">← Back to Home</a>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
